---
// A responsive widget grid for `pageLayout: dashboard` pages. Pairs with
// `Widget.astro` — see /guides/dashboard-widgets/ for usage tips.
//
// `print:grid-cols-1` drops back to a single column when printing: CSS
// Grid pagination across physical page breaks is inconsistently supported
// across print engines, while a plain vertical stack has mature,
// predictable fragmentation behavior everywhere.
---

<div class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-4 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 print:grid-cols-1">
	<slot />
</div>
